Many people are suffering from low calcium levels in their bodies on a regular basis and they tend not to know some of the early warning signs until it is too late. In this article, I will educate you on some of the early signs that indicate that your body needs more calcium.
1. One of the most common signs that you need more calcium in your body is when your bones and joints are easily broken or fractured. If you notice this sign on your body, you should run to your doctor immediately in order to prescribe the right medication and to tell you what food to eat in order to increase your body calcium level.
2. Another sign that you need more calcium in your body is when you notice that you always feel constant muscle pain that does not go away easily. You should endeavour to eat more calcium-rich foods.
3. If you notice that you easily get confused and you easily forget things, you should know that it is one of the signs of low calcium in your body which needs to be avoided immediately.


